Cases in Italy as of 6:00 pm 25 Mar 2020
----------------------------------------
Regarding health monitoring related to the spread of the new coronavirus [SARS-CoV-2] on the national territory, there are 74 386 total cases. At the moment 57 521 people are positive for the virus, 9362 people have recovered. There are 23 112 patients hospitalized with symptoms, in 3489 intensive care, and 30 920 are in home isolation.

There have been 7503 reported deaths, however this number can only be confirmed after the Istituto Superiore di Sanita has established the actual cause of the death.

